<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 00:32:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队中有人决定将这个安静的约旦河西岸地区带入暴力圈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/someone-in-the-idf-decided-to-bring-this-quiet-west-bank-area-into-the-circle-of-violence/0000018c-daf0-daf6-a5df-dffcc42c0000</link><description>一枚以色列国防军导弹射入约旦河西岸难民营中心，造成六名年轻人死亡，七人受伤。军队最初拒绝救护车进入现场，边防警察对伤员拳打脚踢。几天后，军队再次入侵营地</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 20:01:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/someone-in-the-idf-decided-to-bring-this-quiet-west-bank-area-into-the-circle-of-violence/0000018c-daf0-daf6-a5df-dffcc42c0000</guid></item><item><title>年龄：23​​岁；在以色列停留时间：25天；在加沙被扣为人质的时间：90多天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/age-23-time-in-israel-25-days-time-held-hostage-in-gaza-over-90-days/0000018c-d9c6-daf6-a5df-dffe5c260000</link><description>一连几天，都没有比平术赤的踪影。多亏了以色列国防军发布的加沙希法医院的一段视频，他在尼泊尔的家人才得知他被活着带到加沙。三个月后，他在大屠杀中幸存的朋友们重温了恐怖时刻，并参加了拯救他的活动</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 19:26:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/age-23-time-in-israel-25-days-time-held-hostage-in-gaza-over-90-days/0000018c-d9c6-daf6-a5df-dffe5c260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的失败主义者是哈马斯有用的白痴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-defeatists-are-hamas-useful-idiots/0000018c-dac9-ddba-abad-dae9a5d40000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 19:25:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-defeatists-are-hamas-useful-idiots/0000018c-dac9-ddba-abad-dae9a5d40000</guid></item><item><title>犹太-阿拉伯伙伴关系正在以色列建立一个年轻的新和平营</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-jewish-arab-partnership-is-building-a-young-new-peace-camp-in-israel/0000018c-daa9-d751-ad8d-ffadd6e00000</link><description>在加沙战争中，“站在一起”组织进展顺利：它拥有 5,000 名缴纳会费的会员，其学生分会的数量增加了一倍，新的犹太人和阿拉伯人团体正在努力保持团结，并为共同生活注入希望在以色列</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 18:32:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-jewish-arab-partnership-is-building-a-young-new-peace-camp-in-israel/0000018c-daa9-d751-ad8d-ffadd6e00000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗官员试图将致命爆炸归咎于以色列和美国——即使伊斯兰国声称对此负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/iran-pins-deadly-blasts-on-israel-and-u-s-despite-isis-claiming-responsibility/0000018c-dab5-ddba-abad-dab533f60000</link><description>伊朗指挥官表示，“他们只能充当美国政治和犹太复国主义的代理人和雇佣兵”，革命卫队发誓要对周三造成数十人死亡的自杀式爆炸袭击进行报复</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 18:17:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/iran-pins-deadly-blasts-on-israel-and-u-s-despite-isis-claiming-responsibility/0000018c-dab5-ddba-abad-dab533f60000</guid></item><item><title>为什么中国在以色列-哈马斯战争中站在巴勒斯坦一边</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-china-is-siding-with-the-palestinians-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-da8d-ddba-abad-daad516d0000</link><description>中国的信息更多是针对华盛顿而不是耶路撒冷</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 17:25:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-china-is-siding-with-the-palestinians-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-da8d-ddba-abad-daad516d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列真正的胜利图景是绿线两侧的温和</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-real-victory-picture-is-moderation-on-both-sides-of-the-green-line/0000018c-da25-d751-ad8d-ffa510c40000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 16:23:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-real-victory-picture-is-moderation-on-both-sides-of-the-green-line/0000018c-da25-d751-ad8d-ffa510c40000</guid></item><item><title>部长们与以色列陆军参谋长就 10 月 7 日的调查发生冲突后，内塔尼亚胡的政党和甘茨互相指责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-party-gantz-trade-barbs-after-ministers-clash-with-idf-chief-over-oct-7-probe/0000018c-da32-d751-ad8d-ffb60f1e0000</link><description>甘茨在抨击利库德集团和极右翼部长们猛烈抨击以色列国防军 10 月 7 日对军队行为进行的内部调查时表示，“内阁中发生的事情是战争期间出于政治动机的攻击”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 16:11:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-party-gantz-trade-barbs-after-ministers-clash-with-idf-chief-over-oct-7-probe/0000018c-da32-d751-ad8d-ffb60f1e0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦总理致欧盟高级官员：援助加沙防止大规模移民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-pm-to-senior-eu-officials-aid-gaza-to-prevent-mass-migration/0000018c-d9f8-d751-ad8d-fffc90db0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦官员担心加沙地带日益不适宜居住的灾难性状况将导致大规模逃亡。他们声称以色列打算采取国际医疗举措来减少人口</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 15:27:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-pm-to-senior-eu-officials-aid-gaza-to-prevent-mass-migration/0000018c-d9f8-d751-ad8d-fffc90db0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部阿拉伯城市男子遭枪击身亡；北部一女子被发现车内已无生命体征</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/man-fatally-shot-in-arab-city-in-central-israel-woman-found-lifeless-in-car-in-north/0000018c-d957-d751-ad8d-fff732600000</link><description>枪击事件中尚未逮捕任何嫌疑人 ■ 调查该女子死亡原因的警方正在调查可能的性侵犯和谋杀</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 12:14:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/man-fatally-shot-in-arab-city-in-central-israel-woman-found-lifeless-in-car-in-north/0000018c-d957-d751-ad8d-fff732600000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长们公开反对 10 月 7 日对军队行为进行的内部调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-come-out-against-team-set-to-probe-armys-conduct-on-october-7/0000018c-d91c-ddba-abad-dbbd845b0000</link><description>以色列部长们猛烈抨击陆军参谋长领导对哈马斯袭击失败的调查。 “我们正处于战争之中，而你现在就开始调查？”有人说</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 11:45:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-come-out-against-team-set-to-probe-armys-conduct-on-october-7/0000018c-d91c-ddba-abad-dbbd845b0000</guid></item><item><title>他的基布兹宣布，以色列人质于 10 月 7 日被杀，尸体被扣押在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-killed-on-october-7-body-being-held-in-gaza-his-kibbutz-announces/0000018c-d8ea-d751-ad8d-ffee89ab0000</link><description>塔米尔·阿达尔 (Tamir Adar) 是亚法·阿达尔 (Yaffa Adar) 的孙子，亚法·阿达尔 (Yaffa Adar) 也曾在加沙被哈马斯扣押，并通过人质交易获释。战争爆发以来，加沙132名人质中的26名人质已确认死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 10:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-killed-on-october-7-body-being-held-in-gaza-his-kibbutz-announces/0000018c-d8ea-d751-ad8d-ffee89ab0000</guid></item><item><title>随着反对以色列民主的政变停止，推翻内塔尼亚胡的战斗即将来临</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/we-are-well-into-the-day-before-israels-war-in-gaza-ends/0000018c-d626-d751-ad8d-ffa636ef0000</link><description>这位首相的毒药机器在10月7日之后沉寂了几天，现在在他试图保住职位时又恢复了全速运转。他的司法部长亚里夫·莱文（Yariv Levin）仍在继续他的谎言、半真半假和煽动行为</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 04:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/we-are-well-into-the-day-before-israels-war-in-gaza-ends/0000018c-d626-d751-ad8d-ffa636ef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府在北部的承诺可能会让军事力量成为唯一选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-governments-promises-in-north-could-leave-military-force-as-the-only-option/0000018c-d60e-ddba-abad-d6af72280000</link><description>以色列承诺改变北部局势可能会将其推向更广泛的军事对抗 ■ 真主党对哈马斯高级官员被杀的强硬反应将使双方误判</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 04:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-governments-promises-in-north-could-leave-military-force-as-the-only-option/0000018c-d60e-ddba-abad-d6af72280000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军袭击了黎巴嫩南部的真主党行动总部；以色列哈马斯扣押人质的家人抵达卡塔尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-live/israeli-army-establishes-team-to-investigate-hamas-october-7-attacks/0000018c-d781-daf6-a5df-d7fd37c00000</link><description>真主党主席在周五的讲话中警告将对阿鲁里被杀一事进行报复，以色列北部响起了火箭警报。 ■ 他的基布兹称，以色列人质塔米尔·阿达尔于 10 月 7 日被谋杀。与以色列国防军领导人就 10 月 7 日的军队调查发生冲突 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵被杀；至少 133 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙 22,600 人死亡，57,910 人受伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 02:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-live/israeli-army-establishes-team-to-investigate-hamas-october-7-attacks/0000018c-d781-daf6-a5df-d7fd37c00000</guid></item><item><title>即使在哈马斯的囚禁中，她也照亮了整个房间：卡梅尔·盖特仍然在加沙被扣为人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/even-in-captivity-she-lights-up-the-room-carmel-gat-is-still-held-hostage-by-hamas/0000018c-d6a1-ddba-abad-d6a1ba470000</link><description>卡梅尔·盖特以其非凡的力量和决心而闻名。与她一起被哈马斯囚禁的人质说，她通过瑜伽和冥想课程帮助他们保持理智。她的许多朋友要求不要把她抛在后面</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 23:34:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/even-in-captivity-she-lights-up-the-room-carmel-gat-is-still-held-hostage-by-hamas/0000018c-d6a1-ddba-abad-d6a1ba470000</guid></item><item><title>以色列没有实施种族灭绝，但它有种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-isnt-committing-a-genocide-but-it-has-genocidaires/0000018c-d643-daf6-a5df-d77fccc00000</link><description>以色列的行动旨在摧毁哈马斯这个组织，而不是加沙的巴勒斯坦人民。真正让我担心的是以色列政界人士中担任弥赛亚派的高级职务，他们认为这场战争是犹太人民昭然命运的实现</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 22:06:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-isnt-committing-a-genocide-but-it-has-genocidaires/0000018c-d643-daf6-a5df-d77fccc00000</guid></item><item><title>“28 岁时，我被赶出了美国。我必须在日本和以色列之间做出选择”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-05/ty-article/.highlight/i-was-kicked-out-of-america-when-i-was-28-i-had-to-choose-between-japan-and-israel/0000018c-d646-daf6-a5df-d77e9a100000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名日本人和一名美国人来到以色列在战争中表示支持和志愿服务</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 22:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-05/ty-article/.highlight/i-was-kicked-out-of-america-when-i-was-28-i-had-to-choose-between-japan-and-israel/0000018c-d646-daf6-a5df-d77e9a100000</guid></item><item><title>炸毁数百万美元：摩萨德对哈马斯和真主党资金的秘密战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/blowing-up-millions-of-dollars-the-mossads-secret-war-on-hamas-and-hezbollah-funds/0000018c-d5af-daf6-a5df-d7ff58b30000</link><description>多年来，乌迪·利维领导摩萨德的一个部门，负责监控恐怖组织的资金流向。该部队凭借创造性的方法和几乎没有任何限制，成功阻止了向哈马斯和真主党转移巨额资金。然后就被关掉了</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 20:58:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/blowing-up-millions-of-dollars-the-mossads-secret-war-on-hamas-and-hezbollah-funds/0000018c-d5af-daf6-a5df-d7ff58b30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方要求受害者和目击者就哈马斯性暴力问题作证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-ask-victims-and-witnesses-to-testify-about-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018c-d580-d751-ad8d-ffa4acf40000</link><description>10月7日哈马斯性暴力事件的大多数受害者被杀害、被扣为人质或处于心理困扰状态而无法作证。以色列警方调查人员现呼吁公众鼓励活着的受害者或目击者与他们联系并提供证据</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 20:51:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-ask-victims-and-witnesses-to-testify-about-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018c-d580-d751-ad8d-ffa4acf40000</guid></item></channel></rss>